statements and asked questions: 
</p>
<p> (<i>a</i>) Representatives of States members of the Council: Bangladesh, Burkina Faso, 
Canada, Chile, China, Cuba, Egypt (on behalf of the African Group), France (on behalf of the 
European Union), Germany, Japan, Morocco<b>2</b> (on behalf of the Arab Group), Netherlands, 
