Centre, Europe-Third World Centre (also on behalf of Mouvement contre le racisme et pour 
l&#8217;amiti&#233; entre les peuples, the World Federation of Trade Unions and the Women&#8217;s International 
League for Peace and Freedom), Interfaith International, International Humanist and Ethical 
Union (also on behalf of the Association for World Education and the Centre for Enquiry), 
Union de l&#8217;action feminine. 
